{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-blog-post-js","path":"/docker-in-my-WSL/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#install-docker\">Install Docker</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#after-install-docker\">After install Docker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#if-wsl\">If WSL</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#running\">Running</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<h3 id=\"install-docker\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install-docker\" aria-label=\"install docker permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install <a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/\">Docker</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo apt-get update</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo apt remove -y gpg</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo apt install -y gnupg1</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo apt-key add -</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo apt-key fingerprint 0EBFCD88</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo apt-get install software-properties-common -y</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo add-apt-repository \"deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu $(lsb_release -cs) stable\"</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io -y</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"after-install-docker\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#after-install-docker\" aria-label=\"after install docker permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>After install <a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/linux-postinstall/\">Docker</a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo groupadd docker</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo usermod -aG docker $USER</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Logout</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-jstext\">newgrp docker</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo systemctl enable docker</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"if-wsl\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#if-wsl\" aria-label=\"if wsl permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>If <a href=\"https://scotch.io/bar-talk/trying-the-new-wsl-2-its-fast-windows-subsystem-for-linux\">WSL</a></h4>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://nickjanetakis.com/blog/setting-up-docker-for-windows-and-wsl-to-work-flawlessly\">WSL1 can use Docker</a> but I would rather choose to use WSL2</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/wsl2-kernel\">Update WSL1 to WSL2</a></li>\n<li>If you failed to install kernal, just right click to installer and then uninstall and reinstall again. (<a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/WSL/issues/5014\">ref</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"running\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#running\" aria-label=\"running permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Running</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo docker run hello-world</code></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Docker in my WSL","date":"August 18, 2020","spoiler":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/docker-in-my-WSL/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}